{"tid":798701,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【救解答】喺追我嘅人身上見到自己，仲去唔去同暗戀嘅人表白好？！","createTime":"2018-08-29T13:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T13:42:43.000Z","uid":202101,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b2cc2e30ba0a9126d088851a8896cafdef54282e","tid":798701,"uid":202101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:04:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近有個人追緊我，<br />\n日日What's app我，噓寒問暖，<br />\n又成日想約我食飯睇戲，<br />\n但我無咩意思，所以唔喺好想理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有時喺佢身上好似見到自己嘅影子，<br />\n因為我鍾意咗個朋友，<br />\n之前都會成日What's app佢，<br />\n約佢睇下戲，但無表明過啲咩，<br />\n我唔知佢有無feel到我鍾意佢，<br />\n但最近覺得自己同追我嗰個人無咩分別，<br />\n可能我暗戀嘅人都覺得我好煩，唔想理我，<br />\n如果講到好明又怕無朋友做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鍾意就去馬！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女仔要留返啲尊嚴，唔好煩鳩人"},{"pid":"dfd4f8ad65073042abd4d6756ae89b2cad7bbc6f","tid":798701,"uid":202101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似卡住咗咁，進退兩難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664e41dd9fec307a0ad9eef0db3ac0ecf371e819","tid":798701,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:20:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ed6fea3bebf42c5034e42fce6051f556e0c2744","tid":798701,"uid":202101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"664e41dd9fec307a0ad9eef0db3ac0ecf371e819","tid":798701,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB